{"word":"G4065 - περιφρονέω - periphronéō - per-ee-fron-eh'-o - Despise","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιφρονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>periphronéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-fron-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Despise"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசட்டைப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to consider or examine on all sides"},{"paragraph":"2. to set oneself in thought beyond (exalt oneself in thought above) a person or thing; to contemn, despise"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G5426 - φρονέω - phronéō - fron-eh'-o/5426\">G5426</a>; to <i>think beyond</i>, that is, <i>depreciate</i> (<i>contemn</i>): - despise."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2706 - καταφρονέω - kataphronéō - kat-af-ron-eh'-o/2706\">G2706</a>, <a href=\"#/G2707 - καταφροντής - kataphrontḗs - kat-af-ron-tace'/2707\">G2707</a>, <a href=\"#/G4065 - περιφρονέω - periphronéō - per-ee-fron-eh'-o/4065\">G4065</a>"}]}